snippet.title: Fruity Smoothie Gameplay
snippet.description:
13 minutes of..... Fruity Smoothie.

Fruity Smoothie is a co-op game where you grow, throw and shoot fruit all to save your fruit family from evil fruit and vegetables with an identity crisis. So get a friend and get ready to make some smoothies!

http://store.steampowered.com/app/763230/Fruity_Smoothie/

For more gaming, walkthroughs, tips and hilarious commentary subscribe to Heuster - https://www.youtube.com/c/HeusterHeu
